Just a reminder that the people who have fled socialism, communism and government oppression, did NOT vote for Joe Biden, despite the supposed xenophobe in the White House. Your white, bougie lifestyle is coming under attack. Your favorite little brunch spots will close (bring on higher taxes & a national lockdown), oil prices will skyrocket (no more offshore drilling), and purchasing power is going to take a hit.
